                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220522-21-victim205 t18220522-21-viclabel113"></join>. On the 7th of May, my waistcoat hung inside the window. About a quarter before nine o'clock in the morning I saw the prisoner come in at the front door; the shop opens into the passage - he put his right arm in and took the waistcoat off the bar. I pursued him; he was taken by Bow Church, and the waistcoat found in his coat pocket.</p>
